text: Vueltas, or Las Vueltas, may refer to some places: *Vueltas (officially San Antonio de las Vueltas), a village in Villa Clara Province, Cuba *Las Vueltas, a municipality in Chalatenango Department, El Salvador *Vueltas (hill), a hill in Parácuaro Municipality, Michoacán, Mexico ==See also== *Vuelta (disambiguation)
title: Vueltas
